OL,7,FA prison sentence which allows
OL,8,Foffenders to be incarcerated
OL,9,Findefinitely has been branded
OL,10,F"inhumane".
OL,12,FImprisonment for Public Protection
OL,13,F(IPP) sentences were introduced in
OL,14,F2005 before being scrapped in 2012.
OL,16,FHowever, the orders were not revoked
OL,17,Fretrospectively, meaning that two
OL,18,Fdecades since being brought in,
OL,19,Fthousands of people across the UK are
OL,20,Fstill subject to their conditions.
