OL,7,FShirley Debon, Shaun's mother, says
OL,8,Fbehaviour linked to his drug addiction
OL,9,F- which he developed in prison - has
OL,10,Fseen him recalled four times. She says
OL,11,Fhe has now spent 14 years behind bars,
OL,12,FShirley is now campaigning for all
OL,13,Fprisoners still serving an IPP to be
OL,14,Fre-sentenced.
OL,16,F"I don't condone what these people
OL,17,Fhave done, they deserved prison," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
