OL,7,FWhat are IPP sentences?
OL,9,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,10,Fsaid: "It is right that IPP sentences
OL,11,Fwere abolished. We are determined to
OL,12,Fmake progress towards safe and
OL,13,Fsustainable releases for those in
OL,14,Fprison, but not in a way that
OL,15,Fundermines public protection."
